                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>who sold about $150 worth of<lb/> goods on Credit after this he<lb/> swindled them\n                all out of their<lb/> money and goods, the name of<lb/> this young man now escapes\n                me<lb/> but I think if it is necessary<lb/> I can ascertain it. <sic>Hopeing</sic>\n                these<lb/> few lines may be a source of<lb/> information to you in order to<lb/>\n                carry on your controversy I<lb/> remain yours respectfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Louis Potsdamer</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>331 Market St.</placeName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
